Interactive command launcher for Linear workflow commands.

When you run this command, I'll present an interactive picker to help you quickly find and run any Linear workflow command.

## How It Works

**Step 1:** Select a category
- Issue Creation
- Workflow & Status
- Progress & Delivery
- Maintenance & Help

**Step 2:** Select a specific command from that category

**Step 3:** The command runs immediately with any needed prompts

This is the fastest way to discover and use commands without memorizing them!

## Available Commands

**Issue Creation (6 commands)**
- Create bugs, features, improvements, blockers, and sub-tasks

**Workflow & Status (8 commands)**
- Start work, pause, request feedback, check status

**Progress & Delivery (3 commands)**
- Create PRs, post updates, request release approval

**Maintenance & Help (4 commands)**
- Check workflow health, cleanup branches, get help, tutorial

